parameters: Kyaahh!!\| Help!! That Robbin' Goblin is stealing from the market place again!!
When will he learn that thievery is a sin... Perhaps some people can't be saved?
I'll make him pay this time! What's he stealing this time? And what weapons does he have?
That doesn't matter! Just hurry up and get to the market, our great hero!!
The Dogmatika Nation seems to be continuing to grow it's borders! I wonder what's next for our
It's amazing how far the Dogmatika has grown over the years... It brings me to tears seeing how far we've come!
This way is to the Dogmatika Plaza. Events and all sorts that the higher ups enforce will be hosted there...
Apparently we're close to having a big event this week, so the plaza is empty at the minute.
Yet another boring day. Maybe I should enlist in the Dogmatika Army...
Over here is the Inn of the Mystical Elf! They may not have elves in there, but a good night sleep here will make you feel like
you've been healed by one! I still don't know how they get their pillows so comfortable!
